With you?

31
00:02:08,899 --> 00:02:11,127
Now that’s not right.

32
00:02:11,454 --> 00:02:14,168
I’m not sure you should
be smoking marihuana.

33
00:02:14,168 --> 00:02:16,006
This is a wedding.

34
00:02:18,740 --> 00:02:21,740
Just trying to get in the spirit.

35
00:03:17,327 --> 00:03:18,970
This is a new look.

36
00:03:18,970 --> 00:03:21,197
Yeah, yeah. Slept like crap.

37
00:03:22,922 --> 00:03:24,841
Who we calling on here?

38
00:03:24,841 --> 00:03:26,415
Benny Warren Cousins.

39
00:03:26,415 --> 00:03:29,411
We got an arrest warrant for him
from 1969.

40
00:03:29,411 --> 00:03:30,362
What’s the story?

41
00:03:30,362 --> 00:03:33,782
Well, a local Fishtown girl was
found strangled in his apartment.

42
00:03:33,782 --> 00:03:35,191
Eleanor McCormick.

43
00:03:35,191 --> 00:03:36,951
What’d they get from
their first time around?

44
00:03:36,951 --> 00:03:38,258
There wasn’t a first time.

45
00:03:38,258 --> 00:03:41,161
Warren hightailed it to Canada
the night of the murder.

46
00:03:41,161 --> 00:03:42,522
Mounties couldn’t help?

47
00:03:42,522 --> 00:03:43,505
They couldn’t find him.

48
00:03:43,505 --> 00:03:45,804
Think he changed his name up there,
went underground.

49
00:03:45,804 --> 00:03:48,667
No one’s heard word one from him
in 36 years.

50
00:03:48,667 --> 00:03:50,157
What brought him back to Philly?

51
00:03:50,157 --> 00:03:52,050
Father’s funeral.

52
00:03:52,706 --> 00:03:54,968
He’s holed up with an old buddy
in this place.

53
00:03:54,968 --> 00:03:58,186
Busy-body neighbor recognized him.
Called it in.

54
00:03:58,186 --> 00:03:59,526
Let’s go.

55
