Philadelphia PD for Warren Cousins.

56
00:04:22,362 --> 00:04:23,769
I’m Warren.

57
00:04:24,072 --> 00:04:28,054
Warren Cousins, you’re under arrest for
the 1969 murder of Eleanor McCormick.

